    "body": "@Aluminium95 To answer your question directly, I believe various things about the API you want are not possible to type statically. In particular, comm::recv can't know the type of the current task's port (without some major language changes). If we encapsulate actors into a type-parameterized class then such a thing should be possible.\n",
